#: ../../manual/render/cycles/nodes/types/shaders/anisotropic.rst:12
msgid ""
"The *Anisotropic* :abbr:`BSDF (Bidirectional scattering distribution "
"function)` node is used to add a glossy reflection, with separate control "
"over U and V direction roughness. The tangents used for shading are derived "
"from the active UV map. If no UV map is available, they are automatically "
"generated using a sphere mapping based on the mesh bounding box."
msgstr ""

